    <summary>Interface for monitoring the state of an application service.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">Interface for monitoring the state of an application service.  See
 <c><see cref="T:Android.App.Service" /></c> and
 <c><see cref="M:Android.Content.Context.BindService(Android.Content.Intent,Android.Content.IServiceConnection,Android.Content.IServiceConnection)" /></c> for more information.
 </para>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">Like many callbacks from the system, the methods on this class are called
 from the main thread of your process.
</para>
      <para tool="javadoc-to-mdoc">
        <format type="text/html">
          <a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/ServiceConnection.html" target="_blank">[Android Documentation]</a>
        </format>
      </para>
    </remarks>
    <since version="Added in API level 1" />
